data.description: Welcome to modern luxury living at the sought-after 5401 North community! Striking 3 level end-unit townhome offering 3 Bdrm, 3 full baths & half bath on 2nd Fl, it's a true gem. Step inside & be captivated by the sleek LVP flooring that graces both the main & 2nd levels, effortlessly blending style & durability. The kitchen is a culinary masterpiece w/stainless steel appliances, exquisite granite countertops, central island w/bar seating & an inviting dining area. The family room is a luminous oasis w/its open-concept design, ceiling fan & direct access to your private balcony, the perfect spot to savor fresh air & tranquility. On the main floor, you'll find a versatile bedroom complete with full bath catering to your guests' comfort or your work-from-home needs. Venture to the 3rd Fl & you'll discover the owners' suite, a personal sanctuary featuring an opulent WIC, double vanity & tiled walk-in shower. 2nd Bdrm offers WIC & en-suite bath ensuring everyone enjoys their own space. New carpet, fresh interior paint, stylish new light fixtures & a thorough HVAC duct cleaning. Amenities: Clubhouse/pool/gardens & more
